Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.27,0:01:35.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我乃掌管天地伦常的柱之女神
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.78,0:01:40.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将汝 从大地之束缚中解放吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.51,0:01:46.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 构造出公式 意识集中在自己心里而不是施法对象上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.18,0:01:52.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时涌现出来的东西 就是你的魔力
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.20,0:01:54.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己的意识…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.34,0:02:04.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涌现出的东西…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.24,0:02:19.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 浮起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.34,0:02:21.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了 我做到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.94,0:02:23.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 你快看
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.57,0:02:26.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别忘了现在的感觉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.42,0:02:32.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…好 诗寇蒂 这里有个奇怪的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.57,0:02:34.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 哨兵小弟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.68,0:02:37.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真没办法 我去一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.20,0:02:40.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧 仙太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.56,0:02:42.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 为什么突然有了魔力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.28,0:02:48.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对他人的爱怜之心成为了力量之源
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.90,0:02:52.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给予了诗寇蒂魔力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.09,0:02:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧 仙太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.42,0:02:55.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有这种东西在啊 吓了我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.46,0:02:55.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.70,0:02:58.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起了 仙太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.06,0:02:58.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 因为她是女孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.88,0:03:05.78,Chapter,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&HF8B356&}{\3c&H47E7F3&}啊啊 我亲爱的丘比特
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.55,0:03:11.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样 很厉害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.82,0:03:15.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次让你姐姐治好了伤口
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.59,0:03:18.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像魔法师一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.97,0:03:22.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是魔法师 是女神
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.23,0:03:24.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女神？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.19,0:03:30.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是吗 外国人真厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.56,0:03:41.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干…干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.25,0:03:47.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…我不是在看你 只是觉得那个真是厉害…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.22,0:03:49.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像晃得很厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.50,0:03:51.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.86,0:03:54.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 听话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.60,0:03:56.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 掉下来了 掉下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.54,0:04:03.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.69,0:04:06.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失败失败
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.76,0:04:11.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.20,0:04:13.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.25,0:04:19.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是歌声
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.72,0:04:41.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.85,0:04:42.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.41,0:04:44.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.63,0:04:45.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣洁之铃音（holy bell）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.81,0:04:48.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女神都有自己的天使
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.82,0:04:50.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天使…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.97,0:04:54.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 诗寇蒂也有天使吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.16,0:04:58.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有吗 你不是说自己是女神吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.79,0:05:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有啊 你说…说什么呢 当然有了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.58,0:05:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的天使是什么样的？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.07,0:05:11.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出生吧 天使
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.11,0:05:21.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然像姐姐说的那样 要靠自己的力量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.37,0:05:25.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 现在的我一定可以
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.35,0:05:27.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…大概
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.12,0:05:30.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之拜托你了 天使
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.46,0:05:35.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快出生吧 我答应仙太郎明天给他看的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.62,0:05:38.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是力量不够
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.74,0:05:41.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用以前用过的这个法术增幅装置…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.52,0:05:43.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这就不是自己的力量了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.06,0:05:46.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 孵蛋还是要用皮肤接触啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.98,0:05:50.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了 拜托了 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.29,0:05:52.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 还有…还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.08,0:05:59.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么一直吵个不停啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.44,0:06:01.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要练习法术也该…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.74,0:06:10.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊 稍微能用点小法力就去买天使卵…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.75,0:06:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吞下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.37,0:06:15.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吞下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.63,0:06:17.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.66,0:06:25.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要～绝对不要～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.64,0:06:24.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听话 到我房间来一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.56,0:06:28.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用超强力呕吐剂 肯定让你都吐出来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.09,0:06:31.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兀儿德的药肯定会有很奇怪的副作用 绝对不要～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.25,0:06:34.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你自己偷偷摸摸干坏事不好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.09,0:06:36.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是这样 但我绝对不要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.84,0:06:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 快过来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.53,0:06:38.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救我 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.34,0:06:46.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 有什么 在我的体内…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.03,0:06:48.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诗寇蒂 诗寇蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.66,0:06:50.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓓儿丹蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.74,0:06:58.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果就这样让天使卵的力量增大…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.64,0:07:03.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以她现在的力量 很可能会失控
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.95,0:07:08.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 但是如果顺利的话 说不定…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.92,0:07:13.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话虽如此 这样下去诗寇蒂会有危险 还是封印起来比较…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.69,0:07:16.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除非万不得已 否则我不想这么做…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.42,0:07:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓓儿丹蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.59,0:07:25.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诗寇蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.58,0:07:29.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保持清醒 别被力量冲昏头脑了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.31,0:07:35.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了 出来的话就在它实体化之前封印
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.77,0:07:37.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓓儿丹蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.39,0:07:59.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.92,0:08:03.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 兀儿德
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.65,0:08:28.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天使是天使…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.49,0:08:31.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好小
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.82,0:08:36.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 好像顺利继承了诗寇蒂的力量呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.35,0:08:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好累…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.17,0:08:44.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.56,0:08:47.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 诗寇蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.46,0:08:49.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.92,0:08:51.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看你背后
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.10,0:09:01.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐…姐姐 天使…天使在…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.58,0:09:04.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你的天使哦 诗寇蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.04,0:09:07.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.05,0:09:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多关照 天使
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.56,0:09:29.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.24,0:09:46.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是诗寇蒂的天使
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.41,0:09:46.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.25,0:09:48.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她叫高贵之真红（noble scarlet）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.59,0:09:51.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.43,0:09:56.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比你姐姐的天使小多了 她能干些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.69,0:09:59.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能干…什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.33,0:10:04.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（我多嘴了吧）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.54,0:10:09.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总…总之我的天使能做很多事的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.86,0:10:11.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后会让你见识到的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.82,0:10:14.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不用勉强…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.31,0:10:17.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 出发了 仙太郎 高贵之真红
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.98,0:10:58.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.55,0:11:02.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.64,0:11:10.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.30,0:11:13.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是封印起来比较好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.92,0:11:18.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个样子似乎没有失控的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.16,0:11:22.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且有着一颗忠诚于主人的善良之心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.17,0:11:25.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这个问题…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.37,0:11:27.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兀儿德…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.43,0:11:41.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还在意失败的事情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.66,0:11:45.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那没什么大问题的 别放…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.98,0:11:50.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（明天的比赛…）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.49,0:11:52.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（弘明君）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.25,0:11:53.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（要加油哦）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.53,0:11:56.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,KISS…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.91,0:12:01.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 吓我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.74,0:12:04.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诗寇蒂 你的电话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.60,0:12:05.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仙太郎打来的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.21,0:12:09.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.67,0:12:12.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后的微调想让诗寇蒂来做
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.19,0:12:15.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 完美了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.46,0:12:17.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样还输的话就是你技术的问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.55,0:12:21.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我稍微骑下看看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.45,0:12:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害 感觉很顺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.34,0:12:28.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了 本姑娘是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.85,0:12:29.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诗寇蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.85,0:12:32.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 本姑娘就是蓓儿姐的妹妹——天才…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.86,0:12:33.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.70,0:12:36.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有个请求
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.04,0:12:39.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.06,0:12:41.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.33,0:12:45.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你能来看我的比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.49,0:12:48.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天 在最终赛段那里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.96,0:12:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以是可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.71,0:12:52.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在终点吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.92,0:12:54.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里是附近最高的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.18,0:12:57.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以看到整个跑道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.80,0:13:02.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那里的话 我在比赛时也能看到诗寇蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.28,0:13:05.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定会赢的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.33,0:13:06.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.11,0:13:16.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.94,0:13:34.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不是的…这个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.79,0:13:36.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.62,0:13:44.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你都做了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.07,0:13:47.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让仙太郎回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.05,0:13:50.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法做明天的约定…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.67,0:13:52.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他肯定会觉得我是个怪人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.80,0:13:57.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能会讨厌我了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.89,0:14:01.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别过来 出去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.52,0:14:03.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点出去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.54,0:14:16.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 发生了这种事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.04,0:14:19.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以被赶出房间了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.58,0:14:22.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定是想要用自己的方法帮上忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.84,0:14:29.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子不会因为这个就讨厌你的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.90,0:14:33.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等过段时间 明天再去房间看看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.99,0:14:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话 空着手不太好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.54,0:14:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萤一
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.99,0:14:41.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰淇淋店还开着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.86,0:15:15.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高贵之真红…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.18,0:15:19.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是MTP关东公开赛少年组决赛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.95,0:15:22.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下面介绍参赛选手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.35,0:15:25.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2号　箱崎悟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.19,0:15:27.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,57号　山根吉田
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.02,0:15:31.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,18号　川西仙太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.12,0:15:33.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,8号　小枝仁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.31,0:15:49.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经不生气了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.89,0:15:55.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 下次再多管闲事 就把你送回蛋里去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.73,0:16:03.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 冰淇淋 一定是姐姐和萤一吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.34,0:16:06.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那等一下等仙太郎来…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.99,0:16:13.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不用了 不去也…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.52,0:16:19.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仙太郎一定也这么想 不用在意
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.14,0:16:23.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高贵之真红？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.12,0:16:25.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说了不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.72,0:16:29.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 等一下吃冰淇淋 先放到冰箱里…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.96,0:16:39.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,领先的是川西仙太郎！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.31,0:16:40.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能这样一路领先到终点吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.28,0:16:44.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二名箱崎和第三名松本突然摔倒！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.60,0:16:48.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山根选手铲出跑道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.65,0:16:51.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然不减速就进了弯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.94,0:16:52.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他选手能追上么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.26,0:16:54.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比赛变得有趣起来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.83,0:16:55.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然…没来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.15,0:17:03.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么倒在这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.92,0:17:08.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 仙太郎摔倒了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.46,0:17:19.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前轮支架…没有摔坏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.52,0:17:21.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轮毂也没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.17,0:17:22.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辐条…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.25,0:17:23.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.37,0:17:26.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我们一起调整的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.63,0:17:29.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你不是说一定会赢的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.17,0:17:32.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,输了的话决不原谅你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.66,0:17:41.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油 仙太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.86,0:17:50.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来了 看着吧 诗寇蒂 我一定会用它…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.68,0:17:54.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我有女神和天使的加护啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.30,0:17:56.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决不能输
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.19,0:18:00.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有一辆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.07,0:18:03.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.30,0:18:20.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MTP KANTOOPEN少年组冠军
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.56,0:18:22.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,川西仙太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.92,0:18:25.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜 请给他热烈的掌声
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.41,0:18:34.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.82,0:18:38.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高贵之真红？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.83,0:18:43.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…刚才在土丘上…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.66,0:18:47.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算认为我是奇怪的女人也无所谓 只是不想让仙太郎输
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.54,0:18:52.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是太好了 他用我调装的车夺得了冠军
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.29,0:18:54.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.49,0:18:56.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.60,0:19:12.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诗寇蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.26,0:19:17.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她又…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.57,0:19:18.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诗寇蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.00,0:19:21.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.26,0:19:22.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.48,0:19:27.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摔倒的时候我觉得已经不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.34,0:19:30.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是因为诗寇蒂来了 我才能赢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.14,0:19:34.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 你还帮我调整车况
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.87,0:19:38.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一个人是赢不了的 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.95,0:19:40.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个 希望你能收下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.96,0:19:43.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可那是你的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.76,0:19:45.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收下吧 诗寇蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.82,0:19:47.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.22,0:19:54.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…不好意思打扰你们了 我们接下来还要用这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.62,0:19:55.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.31,0:20:07.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的…但是这次看在冰淇淋的份上就原谅你吧 高贵之真红
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.71,0:20:09.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天多谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.36,0:20:12.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 来晚了真抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.18,0:20:15.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.55,0:20:18.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你获胜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.79,0:20:22.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.80,0:20:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那再见
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.18,0:20:26.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.98,0:20:36.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.31,0:20:38.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兀儿德也在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.22,0:20:42.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.67,0:20:46.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是高贵之真红
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.65,0:20:50.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.20,0:20:54.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天使对主人是绝对服从的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.73,0:20:57.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人说的话一定会遵从
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.55,0:21:02.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会 因为我说了…要把她送回蛋里？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.09,0:21:06.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 我喜欢你的啊 想和你在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.09,0:21:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想让你一直在我身边
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.87,0:21:12.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 那孩子一定也是这么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.83,0:21:18.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是要拥有天使就必须知道自己的弱点 有面对一切的坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.65,0:21:21.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那为什么 为什么不告诉我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.18,0:21:24.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她可附不了其他人的身
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.52,0:21:26.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为天使就是自己的一面镜子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.82,0:21:34.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 你只要保持着现在的心情 当拥有了那份坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.68,0:21:36.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天使一定会回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.36,0:21:39.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高贵之真红
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.26,0:21:51.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.51,0:21:53.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.64,0:21:54.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.18,0:21:57.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？高贵之真红呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.09,0:22:02.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微…有段时间不能见面了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.24,0:22:03.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.79,0:22:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当我更加努力 成为大人以后 她会再来见我的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.36,0:22:12.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.58,0:22:17.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能快点见到就好了呢 和高贵之真红
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.63,0:23:57.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我说了滚出去…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.56,0:23:58.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别在意
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.60,0:24:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都很担心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.43,0:24:02.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 都是因为我
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.06,0:24:05.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回 啊啊 半神半魔的我？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.26,0:24:07.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个烂好人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.24,0:24:09.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说谁？
